<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#271f15e98f955f9fa5c3cfb6a958e7a1>.
<#271f15e98f955f9fa5c3cfb6a958e7a1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/75076d38-25e6-4ad6-9cb9-878708728f93>;
