<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/762376b4-1f11-4d40-a4c6-865c98ae3765> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__76293.
_:b0__76293 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
