    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-view.smhi.se/met-obs/ACMF.radande_vader_momentan_view/wms?service=wms&request=getcapabilities>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/metobs/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/hitta-data-for-en-plats/ladda-ner-vaderobservationer/presentWeather>, <https://opendata-download-metobs.smhi.se/api/version/latest/parameter/13.json>, <urn:uuid:4aa4916a-da9a-1bd9-787f-ecb1d8790ca6>, <urn:uuid:9c85dfde-9e35-65fa-4b50-12b98b9db3e2>, <urn:uuid:ef7d338d-344b-c96b-c0b1-0113161189bc>, <urn:uuid:4bbc1d0d-1f47-a652-a006-efbddd749609>;
