<https://doi.org/10.5878/002105> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021003153>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Mediebarometern genomfördes första gången 1979 och har sedan dess genomförts varje år. Undersökningen avser att belysa hur stor andel av den svenska befolkningen som en genomsnittlig dag tagit del av ett antal enskilda medier. Syftet är att beskriva tendenser och förändringar i människors utnyttjande av massmedier.\n\nSyfte:\n\nBeskriva tendenser och förändringar i människors nyttjande av massmedier."@sv, "The first Media Barometer was conducted in 1979 and since then the survey has been carried out annually. The purpose is to explore how the Swedish population is using different media during an average day.\n\nPurpose:\n\nDescribe the trends and changes in people's use of mass media."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002105#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2014-07-10T15:24:02Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002105>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2020-02-14T10:32:11Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Mediebarometern 2011"@sv, "Media Barometer 2011"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__7310.
_:b0__7310 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2011"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2011"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/002105> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
