_:b0__71482 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((12.52 66.35,23.24 66.35,23.24 56.13,12.52 56.13,12.52 66.35))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
