<#d1a7e4d03ca7dbdbf1789c327be9aa9c> {
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/c6830c65-edfc-4509-8099-6536e3f851ee> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/UNKNOWN>;
