    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-19T06:21:51.341Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#3f9813693c78258b2ff77af9116fdc33> {
<https://doi.org/10.23695/A340-J629> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Language Technology (Computational Linguistics)"@en, "corpus"@en;
