<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#20a56808a9bf765db151a66293e70c11>.
<#20a56808a9bf765db151a66293e70c11> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/ce89ba58-f397-47a4-8493-8b5c711fd1ab>;
